data.description:
Welcome to your future home in the highly sought-after Peoria Unified School District! This meticulously maintained gem boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering a cozy retreat with crystal ceiling fans throughout. The brand-new A/C ensures optimal comfort year-round.
Plus, entertain effortlessly in the backyard oasis, perfect for hosting gatherings with drapes to enclose the private patio and enhance the setting. The kitchen features like-new stainless steel appliances, adding a touch of modern elegance. As a bonus, the seller offers a $1,000 flooring credit, allowing you to personalize this home to your taste. Upgrades and charming details make this home unique. Located in a prime no HOA setting, don't miss the opportunity to own this upgraded haven.
